OL,3,CComedians unite for Aigburth teen's
OL,4,Curgent treatment fundraiser
OL,6,FA special comedy night is being held
OL,7,Fto raise urgent funds for Aigburth
OL,8,Fteenager Jake McGregor-How, who needs
OL,9,Flife-saving treatment for a rare
OL,10,Fdegenerative condition.
OL,12,F16-year-old Jake began experiencing
OL,13,Fbalance problems at age 11.
OL,15,FAfter years of tests, he was diagnosed
OL,16,Fat the end of 2025 with Friedreich's
OL,17,FAtaxia, a rare, progressive disease
OL,18,Fthat affects mobility, balance,
OL,19,Fcoordination, and can cause heart and
OL,20,Fsensory problems.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
