PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777838749
OL,3,CComedians unite for Aigburth teen's
OL,4,Curgent treatment fundraiser
OL,6,FJake's father, Paul How, said: "His
OL,7,Fcondition will deteriorate,
OL,8,Fpotentially quite rapidly, which is
OL,9,Fwhy we need to fundraise for this drug
OL,10,Fas quickly as possible.
OL,12,F"Time really is of the essence." The
OL,13,Ffamily has already raised over
OL,14,F#100,000 but still has a long way to
OL,15,Fgo."
OL,17,FJake is supported by the children's
OL,18,Fcharity Tree of Hope, which helps
OL,19,Ffamilies fundraise for treatments not
OL,20,Favailable on the NHS.
OL,26,@nD@`OUtD@`O]
